00:17:45.840 --> 00:17:54.840
Now, where most agent frameworks have you wiring up DAGs and workflows, Agentfield lets you build AI agents the way you build FastAPI microservices.

00:17:55.500 --> 00:17:59.040
Think typed Python functions that become autonomous services.

00:17:59.420 --> 00:18:07.360
They discover each other at runtime, call each other like APIs, scale independently, fail independently, and recover on their own.

00:18:07.360 --> 00:18:08.300
And here's the thing.

00:18:08.620 --> 00:18:10.760
You're not just orchestrating LLM calls.

